article.headline: Texas-San Antonio 60, Georgia St. 48
article.story: SAN ANTONIO -- Travis Gabbidon scored 16 points and had seven rebounds to lead Texas-San Antonio to a 60-48 victory over Georgia State on Saturday night. Omar Johnson added 13 points and five assists, while Morris Smith IV scored 10 points for the Roadrunners (5-4). Joe Dukes and Trae Goldston were the only two players to score in double figures for Georgia State (3-9). Dukes had 11 points, and Goldston scored 10. Texas-San Antonio had a 28-10 advantage in points off turnovers.
